\c 147
\s Rumbidzai Jehovha nokuti tsitsi dzake dzinoonekwa pose-pose
\p
\v 1 Hareruya. Nokuti zvakanaka kuti Mwari wedu aimbirwe nziyo dzokurumbidza; zvinofadza, uye kurumbidza kwakafanira.
\p
\v 2 Jehovha anovaka Jerusarema; anounganidza vakadzingwa VaIsraeri.
\v 3 Anoporesa vane moyo yakaputsika, anosunga mavanga avo.
\v 4 Anotara kuwanda kwenyeredzi; anodzipa dzese mazita adzo.
\v 5 Ishe wedu mukuru, anesimba guru; njere dzake hadziperi.
\v 6 Jehovha anobatsira vanyoro.
\p
\v 7 Imbirai Jehovha muchimuvonga, imbirai Mwari wedu nziyo dzokurumbidza nembira.
\v 8 Iye anofukidza denga namakore, anogadzirira pasi mvura, anomeresa uswa pamakomo.
\v 9 Anopa zvipfuwo zvokudya zvazvo, navana vamakunguvo, anochema.
\v 10 Haafadzwi nesimba rebhiza; haafariri makumbo omurume.
\v 11 Jehovha anofara navanomutya, navanotarira tsitsi dzake.
\p
\v 12 Rumbidza Jehovha, iwe Jerusarema; rumbidza Mwari wako, iwe Ziyoni.
\v 13 Nokuti wakasimbisa mazariro amasuwo ako; akaropafadza vana vako mukati mako.
\v 14 Anoisa rugare panyika yako; anokugutisa nezviyo zvakaisvonaka.
\v 15 Anotuma mirairo yake panyika; shoko rake rinomhanya kwazvo.
\v 16 Anopa vanhu chando samakushe amakwai, anoparadzira chando samadota.
\v 17 Anokanda chimvuramabwe chake sezvimedu; ndianiko angamira pachando chake?
\v 18 Anotuma shoko rake, ndokuzvinyausa; anovhuvhutisa mhepo yake mvura ndokuyerera.
\v 19 Anozivisa Jakove shoko rake, naIsraeri mitemo yake nezvaakatonga.
\v 20 Haana kutongoitira rumwe rudzi saizvozvo; kana zviri zvaakatonga, havana kuzviziva. Hareruya!
